  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IDPs in Paletwa Chin State, Myanmar Need Your Help</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The ongoing armed clashes between the Arakan Army and the Tatmadaw, Myanmar&apos;s Armed Forces, have left the people of Myanmar in desperation. Forced to leave their homes, and became internally displaced persons (IDPs), at IDPs camps at Sahmi, Paletwa Chin State. With this project, we will help save 9000 people who are directly affected and nearly 60,000 people indirectly affected by the ongoing military conflict by providing food, hygienic products and other necessity supplies for them to survive.</narrative>
  </description>
